## Question 8

grep theoretically should be able to tell you the amount of times Dursley is present by highlighting all of the occasions in the terminal (using the code `grep Dursley text_file.txt`), however this code is not highlighting the word on my laptop `grep -o Dursley text_file.txt` will show all of the occasions of Dursley without the context of the file. `grep -c Dursley text_file.txt` will give the number of lines in which Dursley is mentioned.

